{"tid":50626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【柏林恐襲】特朗普再抽水： 證明我想禁絕穆斯林是100%正確","createTime":"2016-12-22T14:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T01:33:24.000Z","uid":22736,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73521140e63588c509a948cf7a0684fb4728aa17","tid":50626,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:50:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161222&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56078192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161222%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56078192&d=3k9qFdqOAHnmvG%2BdGGqsOwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=bbc37027\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161222%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56078192&h=a8cdb077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161222&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56078192</a><br />\n德國柏林周一發生貨車衝入聖誕市集、造成12死50傷的恐襲，美國候任總統特朗普當日已立即將恐襲矛頭指向「伊斯蘭恐怖分子」。他今天再回應時，表明其禁絕穆斯林政策是「100%正確」。<br />\n特朗普周三表示：「你們知道我的計劃的，由始至終也證明了我是正確的，100%正確。<br />\n他在柏林恐襲發生當天，曾提到：「『伊斯蘭國』（IS）及其他伊斯蘭恐怖分子，在他們的社區及宗教場所不斷屠殺基督徒，作為他們全球聖戰的一部分，這些恐怖分子及他們在全球各地的網絡，一定要從地球上徹底剷除。」被問到會否擔心有關言論觸發宗教緊張時，他即改口不提伊斯蘭教及基督教的衝突問題，只是稱恐襲是「對人性的攻擊，而且必須停止」。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBkHau9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBkHau9.jpg&h=19b32bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抵佢得戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee11aabbc1fd1ae29411b42a3a760432a20ce8f","tid":50626,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43d0e28301d839b9ddbf017ed75ac390a9a3c0a6","tid":50626,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"高登仔治國嘅現實版"},{"pid":"e22f1c4700bf7755f3c65ad2814e0444aa18f17b","tid":50626,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as